    scienceEn: `Pedersen & Febbraio (2012) established the myokine concept: muscles are endocrine organs. BDNF released by muscle contraction promotes hippocampal neurogenesis. Fascia research (Schleip, 2003) revealed fascia contains abundant nerve endings deeply involved in proprioception and pain perception.`,
